name: HaikuReader
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: haiku reader
des: What is a Haiku? Hear examples with Haiku Reader. It randomly selects one of ten haikus programmed to be read out loud, one per each request. To access this app, either ask or tell Haiku Reader to read or say any one of the ten haikus.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
